name: Custom Seal Embosser
description:
Seal Embossing Stamp – Stainless Steel, compact design with interchangeable plate insert. Perfect for adding a sophisticated touch to wedding invites, personal branding, corporate stationery, envelopes / return addresses and certificates. Can be folded away neatly when not in use.

Bronze seal plate – 45mm diameter, machine-engraved.

Only to be used on paper stock up to 200gsm.
Excessive force may damage the inner mechanism.

TOP: Most commonly used for Letterheads
BOTTOM: for use on envelopes and stationery. 

It is important that you choose the correct position based on the direction in which you will be using your embosser, as this cannot be changed afterwards.

name: 100 Custom Address Labels
description:
Upon Order, 100 address labels will be custom made for your address (or address of your choice; if gift). 

When ordering:
PAYPAL CUSTOMERS: In note to seller please specify address desired for labels, as well as colors, or any other preferences along with your email address.
CARDHOLDERS: If different from BILLING address, provide  desired address when entering the SHIPPING address.

To make changes or corrections to your order after it has been placed, email belovedcustoms@gmail.com
